select CONVERT(varchar, dpib010.pers_nr) as 'pers_nr', dpib010.naam_samen + ', ' + dpib010.e_roepnaam as 'vol_nm', e_vrlt, dpib010.e_roepnaam, dpib010.vrvg_samen, dpib010.naam_samen, func_kd, func_oms, oe_kort_nm, oe_vol_nm, indnst_dt, uitdnst_dt From dpib010 inner join dpic300 on dpic300.pers_nr = dpib010.pers_nr inner join dpib023 on dpib023.pers_nr = dpib010.pers_nr left join dpic351 on dpic351.func_kd = dpic300.primfunc_kd order by dpib010.pers_nr

SELECT convert(varchar, tpersoon.pers_nr) as 'pers_nr', tpersoon.e_roepnaam + ' ' + tpersoon.naam_samen as 'vol_nm', tpersoon.e_vrlt, tpersoon.e_roepnaam, tpersoon.vrvg_samen, tpersoon.naam_samen, tfunctie.func_oms, tafdeling.oe_vol_nm, tcontract.indnst_dt, tcontract.uitdnst_dt FROM dpib010 tpersoon INNER JOIN dpic300 tcontract ON tcontract.pers_nr = tpersoon.pers_nr INNER JOIN dpib023 tafdeling ON tafdeling.pers_nr = tpersoon.pers_nr INNER JOIN dpic351 tfunctie ON tfunctie.func_kd = tcontract.primfunc_kd WHERE tcontract.uitdnst_dt > getdate() ORDER BY tcontract.indnst_dt

SELECT convert(varchar, tpersoon.pers_nr) as 'pers_nr', tpersoon.e_roepnaam + ' ' + tpersoon.naam_samen as 'vol_nm', tpersoon.e_vrlt, tpersoon.e_roepnaam, tpersoon.vrvg_samen, tpersoon.naam_samen, tfunctie.func_oms, tafdeling.oe_vol_nm, tcontract.indnst_dt, tcontract.uitdnst_dt FROM dpib010 tpersoon INNER JOIN dpic300 tcontract ON tcontract.pers_nr = tpersoon.pers_nr INNER JOIN dpib023 tafdeling ON tafdeling.pers_nr = tpersoon.pers_nr INNER JOIN dpic351 tfunctie ON tfunctie.func_kd = tcontract.primfunc_kd WHERE tcontract.uitdnst_dt < getdate() ORDER BY tcontract.indnst_dt
